{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":10294,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"站着上课","timestamp":1592791219,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10300,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 课已经上完了，是说一直站着吗","timestamp":1592791260,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10306,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我也一样，腰椎有点痛。不过讲道理现在的人身体没点毛病都不好意思说自己是学生","timestamp":1592791284,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10311,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"趴在床上按下腰部比较不舒服的地方 能明显感觉到不舒服的腰椎中间和正常的两块腰椎之间按下的感受不一样 这种一半就有点腰椎上的问题了","timestamp":1592791316,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10315,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"运动🐶","timestamp":1592791341,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10319,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"直接去看一看吧","timestamp":1592791376,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10356,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: dz在北京，并不太想去医院啊，你懂的","timestamp":1592791687,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10359,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 试了试，好像没啥特别的感觉","timestamp":1592791732,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10654,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"试试 “小燕飞”？ （一种动作，我的高中同学在高中就腰间盘突出了 好像这个动作能缓解一些） 然后多睡眠 或者尝试一下keep的腰部舒展？","timestamp":1592794090,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10762,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果是腰椎间盘突出，坐的时间长了，你的腿也会痛，你可以试一下。。。","timestamp":1592795088,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10833,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"现在课也上好了，就减少坐在电脑前的时间吧，坚持做一些轻柔的活动。对楼上有同感，我大三的时候突然感到腿部从骨头往外发散的痛，痛起来走路都得歇着，但是腰并不疼。去医院检查不出来，大夫后来说你拍个腰部的片子吧，然后就发现有椎间盘膨出。之后就是打腺苷钴胺，打了两天就好了（坚持多打了几天）","timestamp":1592795735,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":10839,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":1912,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"游泳游泳游泳！","timestamp":1592795795,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":6,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":1912,"reply":12,"tag":null,"text":"上了一学期网课感觉腰不太舒服，就隐隐作痛......请问各位有没有什么自检自查腰椎是否出问题的办法呢？以及下一步该怎么办？","timestamp":1592791201,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}